## Task Details

### T-001: Initial Data Model
**Priority:** high
**Problem:** No database schema defined yet.
**Solution:** Design Prisma schema based on domain requirements.
**Files:** `prisma/schema.prisma`
**Acceptance Criteria:**
- [ ] All entities with relationships defined
- [ ] Indexes on frequently queried fields
- [ ] Migration runs cleanly: `npx prisma migrate dev --name init`

### T-002: Public Pages
**Priority:** high
**Problem:** No public-facing UI.
**Solution:** Build listing + detail pages as Server Components.
**Files:** `app/(public)/`, `components/public/`
**Acceptance Criteria:**
- [ ] Responsive layout (mobile-first)
- [ ] {{ language | capitalize }} UI text
- [ ] Server Components with `force-dynamic`

### T-003: Admin Panel
**Priority:** high
**Problem:** No admin interface.
**Solution:** Build login, dashboard, CRUD pages.
**Files:** `app/admin/`, `components/admin/`, `lib/auth.ts`
**Acceptance Criteria:**
- [ ] JWT auth with protected routes
- [ ] Dashboard with overview stats
- [ ] CRUD operations for all entities

### T-004: API Endpoints
**Priority:** high
**Problem:** No REST API.
**Solution:** Build CRUD endpoints with auth middleware.
**Files:** `app/api/`
**Acceptance Criteria:**
- [ ] Transactions for related mutations
- [ ] Proper HTTP status codes
- [ ] Auth required for write operations
{% if use_docker %}

### T-005: Docker Deployment
**Priority:** high
**Problem:** No production deployment config.
**Solution:** Multi-stage Dockerfile + Traefik config.
**Files:** `Dockerfile`, `docker-compose.traefik.yml`
**Acceptance Criteria:**
- [ ] `prisma generate` in both deps AND builder stages
- [ ] Health check endpoint
- [ ] Traefik labels for SSL
{% endif %}

